'''Nɛrɛ''' walima '''nɛ̀rɛ''' (''Parkia biglobosa'') ye [[sahɛli]] jamana [[yiri]] madonnen ye. Nafa caman bɛ sɔrɔ nɛrɛ la. Misali la, a mugu bɛ don, a kolo bɛ kɛ [[sunbala]] ye. Sunbalaji bɛ [[dilan]] ni sunbala ye. Sunbalaji makadi kosobɛ [[Mali]] kɔnɔ. O de kɔsɔn, najini dilannaw ye najini dɔ dilana k'o tɔgɔ wele sunbalani. [[Kɛnɛyatigilama]]w y'a sɛminciya, sɛgɛsɛgɛli caman kɔnɔfɛ, k'a jɔyɔrɔ ka bon hali [[kɛnɛya]] sabati la. Sanko joli cayabana bɛ mɔgɔ minu na ani bugu dalen don minu ɲana yeli la.


